WEBVTT

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:02.216
And most importantly to them,

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:04.240
how would others view them?

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:07.216
Over the last three years

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:11.136
of having numerous conversations
with friends of mine

00:11:11.160 --> 00:11:15.096
and also complete strangers
from around the world,

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:17.816
I learned some really important things

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:21.560
about how African-American women
identify with their hair.

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:24.776
And so when I think back

00:11:24.800 --> 00:11:28.336
to that hiring manager in Mobile, Alabama,

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:31.096
I'd say, "Actually, no.